<td align="center"><b>
<i>Calliopsis callops</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cockerell and Porter, 1899&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Hypomacrotera callops </i>Cockerell and Porter, 1899</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Andrenidae">Andrenidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Calliopsis">Calliopsis</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Calliopsis">Calliopsis</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Hypomacrotera&name=Calliopsis&flags=subgenus:"><i>Hypomacrotera</i></a></small>
</td></tr></table><p>
